_sText: dm_austere_facility By: Natalya[AF] Map Features: - 48 Spawns - Cubemaps - Radar Map - Custom Textures This is the exact same as gg_austere_facility except for I've moved the spawns around so that it can be used for Death Match. There aren't any other differences. The textures are the skybox (look up in the main area to see stars) and a counter top in the tunnel area. It also has built in some skins for various props including the vending machines, van, pickup truck, and some other small stuff in the tunnels. The skins shouldn't show up on other maps and won't override any customs you have when you go to another map so don't worry about that happening. They will show up here only. Inspiration came from this map: gg_underground_z But all the work in my map is 100% mine and original. I didn't actually take anything out of underground z aside from ideas. Thanks to Seraphim for helping error test it. Anyway... I hope y'all enjoy the map.
